---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="readme-container">
    <div class="readme-content">
      <h1>Pxltr</h1>
      <p><em>Freelance Developer & Artist</em></p>
      <div class="badges">
        <a href="https://github.com/your-username" target="_blank"><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/github-%23121011.svg?style=for-the-badge&logo=github&logoColor=white" alt="GitHub"></a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/your-username" target="_blank"><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/linkedin-%230077B5.svg?style=for-the-badge&logo=linkedin&logoColor=white" alt="LinkedIn"></a>
        <a href="https://www.artstation.com/your-username" target="_blank"><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/artstation-%23191919.svg?style=for-the-badge&logo=artstation&logoColor=white" alt="ArtStation"></a>
      </div>
      <p>Hi, I'm Pxltr, a creative soul who loves to build beautiful and functional things. I specialize in web development and digital art.</p>
      <h2>Table of Contents</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
        <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
      <h2 id="about">About Me</h2>
      <p>I'm a passionate developer and artist with a knack for creating engaging experiences. I have a strong background in front-end development and a love for creating beautiful and intuitive user interfaces. When I'm not coding, you can find me sketching, painting, or exploring new creative mediums.</p>
      <h2 id="skills">Skills</h2>
      <h3>Development</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>HTML, CSS, JavaScript</li>
        <li>React, Vue, Svelte</li>
        <li>Node.js, Express</li>
        <li>Python, Django</li>
        <li>SQL, MongoDB</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Art & Design</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>UI/UX Design</li>
        <li>Illustration</li>
        <li>Branding</li>
        <li>Adobe Creative Suite</li>
      </ul>
      <h2 id="projects">Projects</h2>
      <p>Here are a few of my recent projects:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Project 1:</strong> A web-based application for managing tasks and projects.</li>
        <li><strong>Project 2:</strong> A series of digital illustrations for a children's book.</li>
        <li><strong>Project 3:</strong> A branding and identity design for a local startup.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2 id="contact">Contact</h2>
      <p>I'm always open to new opportunities and collaborations. Feel free to reach out to me via email or social media.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:youremail@example.com">youremail@example.com</a></li>
        <li><strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/your-username" target="_blank">github.com/your-username</a></li>
        <li><strong>LinkedIn:</strong> <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/your-username" target="_blank">linkedin.com/in/your-username</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  body {
    background-color: #0d1117;
    color: #c9d1d9;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji";
  }

  .readme-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    border: 1px solid #30363d;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .readme-content {
    padding: 45px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .badges {
    margin-top: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .badges img {
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  a {
    color: #58a6ff;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  pre {
    background-color: #161b22;
    padding: 16px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  code {
    font-family: "SFMono-Regular", Consolas, "Liberation Mono", Menlo, Courier, monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
</style>